cache_ro_type_description_raid_0	=	"RAID 0 requires two or more SSDs. This configuration increases performance and capacity but provides no fault tolerance. A single SSD failure will result in the SSD cache being unable to accelerate random I/O; however, no data will be lost. RAID 0 makes for a practical choice if there are cost considerations."
