cache_safe_crash_desc	=	"<span class="orange-status">SSD Cache {0} on Volume {1} has crashed, but data have been synced.</span> Data are still accessible because Automatic Protection Mechanism has synced the data to the corresponding HDD. However, new data will not be written in this SSD cache. We recommend going to SSD Cache {0} and clicking <div class="sm-pool-sug-more-btn-img"></div> > <b>Remove</b> to remove this SSD cache and then create a new one."
